data.meta_description: Bartholomaus Gr V Starhemberg-Schaunberg-Efferdi was born in the year 1625 in Riedegg (Oberösterreich) Au, son of Gundakar Count Of Starhemberg and Anna Sabine Barones Van Dietrichstein. He was married on December 30, 1650 in Windischgraetz (Steiermark) Au to Esther Baroness Of Windischgraetz-Waldstein, they had 4 children. He died on March 22, 1676 in Wien, Österreich. This information is part of Family tree Baris by Paul Baris on Genealogy Online.
